 1917 Wednesday 7 Feb. On duti as usual , kept go pretti well all day . Sapper Maroni on sandbag the wall . A coupl of stretcher case come in midst of the confus . " One thing you must not do , let the fire out ." A rush of 5 patient no excus . Ridgi give Toni his balaclava from me . T. not too good . Gener beggar up . Rum issu song , Rumour of big raid short . Wrote to May Miss Wilson
